Our Process

From initial consultation to final certification, we ensure every project is completed to the highest standards with clear communication every step of the way.

Consultation & Quote

We start with a thorough assessment of your needs. Whether it's an EV charger, pool electrical, or smart home system, we provide detailed quotes and expert recommendations tailored to your project.

Design & Planning

Our team creates a comprehensive electrical plan that meets all safety codes and your specific requirements. We handle permits, compliance, and coordinate with other trades if needed.

Professional Installation

Licensed electricians execute the work with precision and care. We use quality materials, follow best practices, and keep your property clean and tidy throughout the installation process.

Testing & Certification

Every installation undergoes rigorous testing and certification. We provide all necessary documentation, warranties, and a full walkthrough to ensure you're confident with your new electrical system.

Powering Auckland's future with specialist electrical solutions. Licensed, certified, and committed to excellence.
